DESCRIPTION:Donald Schleicher\, conductor\; Shihan Jin\, graduate assistan
 t conductor\nCentering the program is Igor Stravinsky’s monumental Le sa
 cre du printemps (The Rite of Spring)\, infamous for its avant-garde music
  and ballet choreography. A lighter take on the season is Lili Boulanger
 ’s vivacious yet introspective D’un matin de printemps (Of a Spring Mo
 rning). Richard Strauss’s Don Juan\, Op. 20 depicts the legendary ill-fa
 ted bachelor.\nLili Boulanger\, D’un matin de printemps (Of a Spring Mor
 ning)\nRichard Strauss\, Don Juan\, Op. 20\nIgor Stravinsky\, Le sacre du 
 printemps (The Rite of Spring)
